name: Unexpected Way Home
description:
You're a woman that lives in Mexico. At night, on your way back home from university your car stops working, so now you have to find another way home. But you have to remember how dangerous it is for woman outside, especially at night. 

Features:

  • 7 different endings.
  • Available in Spanish.
  • Available in English.
  • Game length: about 10 min unlocking all the endings.

This was a school project based on our city in Mexico. Made by Team Sukusa. (Might receive an update in the future).
